OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1782488897
OL,3,CTapestry celebrating Ukraine and
OL,4,Ccalling for peace displayed in
OL,5,CDumfries church
OL,7,FA tapestry celebrating Ukraine and the
OL,8,Fcountry's fight for freedom has been
OL,9,Funveiled at a Dumfries church.
OL,11,FThe Unity Rushnik ` Victory Rushnik is
OL,12,Fan international project to create a
OL,13,Ftapestry to unite Ukrainians worldwide
OL,14,Fand honour Ukrainian culture.
OL,16,FA rushnik is a traditional ceremonial
OL,17,Fcloth used across East Slavic cultures
OL,18,Flike Ukraine.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
