PN,32102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1782488897
OL,3,CTapestry celebrating Ukraine and
OL,4,Ccalling for peace displayed in
OL,5,CDumfries church
OL,7,FThe Unity Rushnik - Victory Rushnik
OL,8,Fhas been created by Ukrainians and
OL,9,Fpeople across the world, who have
OL,10,Fcontributed their own parts to the
OL,11,Fover 160metre-long fabric scroll,
OL,12,Fincluding the Ukrainian community in
OL,13,FDumfries.
OL,15,FDr Tatyana Bondarenko is one of the
OL,16,Fchurch's Ukrainian parishioners, and
OL,17,Fshe lead the project.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,322,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1782488897
OL,3,CTapestry celebrating Ukraine and
OL,4,Ccalling for peace displayed in
OL,5,CDumfries church
OL,7,FShe told ITV Border: "Dumfries opened
OL,8,Fits heart to many Ukrainians who have
OL,9,Fstayed here for a long time. We would
OL,10,Flike to say thank you, by displaying
OL,11,Fthis piece of art in the church.
OL,13,F"The main idea is to make this
OL,14,Ftapestry longer - we've created a big
OL,15,FDumfries piece, where local people
OL,16,Fwere involved. We invited the ladies
OL,17,Ffrom the local embroidery group, to
OL,18,Fjoin our piece to the big one.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,322,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1782488897
OL,3,CTapestry celebrating Ukraine and
OL,4,Ccalling for peace displayed in
OL,5,CDumfries church
OL,7,F"For us, it's pivotally important
OL,8,Fbecause we are surviving now. We would
OL,9,Flike to show, we try to do our best.
OL,10,FWe've tried to join all Ukrainians
OL,11,Faround the world to help Ukraine."
OL,13,FAnnette Beagrie, chair of St John's
OL,14,Fvestry, said: "We're hugely blessed by
OL,15,Fhaving the Ukrainians as part of our
OL,16,Fchurch family here. The fact that they
OL,17,Fwant to bring this to St John's as
OL,18,Fpart of its journey is amazing. It's
OL,19,Fbeen really super to receive it here,
OL,20,Fand the Ukrainians are so important to
OL,21,Fus.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,322,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1782488897
OL,3,CTapestry celebrating Ukraine and
OL,4,Ccalling for peace displayed in
OL,5,CDumfries church
OL,7,F"You can't miss it, it's fantastic!
OL,8,FIt's been all over Europe, and tonight
OL,9,Fsome of the local Ukrainians are
OL,10,Fadding their parts to it.
OL,12,F"You've got to see it to believe it."
OL,14,FThe artwork has already visited 12
OL,15,Fcountries, and will be on display at
OL,16,FSt John the Evangelist in Dumfries
OL,17,Funtil 1 July.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
